pg 315w,\n/static/3a084e15bae64be25626ecd07de1c2de/07854/quickselection.jpg 534w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 534px) 100vw, 534px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>A moving dashed line, commonly referred to as the ‚Äúmarching ants,‚Äù will automatically show the areas marked by the tool.\nRefine the Selection with a Quick Mask\nPress the <strong><em>Q key</em></strong> on the keyboard to enter <strong><em>Quick Mask mode</em></strong>. This step applies a red overlay over the areas that are not selected.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/42423f1ce6c0a3c6028a618434789650/eea4a/quickmaskmode.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.86075949367089%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"quick mask mode\"\n        title=\"quick mask mode\"\n        src=\"/static/42423f1ce6c0a3c6028a618434789650/828fb/quickmaskmode.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/42423f1ce6c0a3c6028a618434789650/ff44c/quickmaskmode.jpg 158w,\n/static/42423f1ce6c0a3c6028a618434789650/a6688/quickmaskmode.jpg 315w,\n/static/42423f1ce6c0a3c6028a618434789650/828fb/quickmaskmode.jpg 630w,\n/static/42423f1ce6c0a3c6028a618434789650/0ede0/quickmaskmode.jpg 945w,\n/static/42423f1ce6c0a3c6028a618434789650/3ac88/quickmaskmode.jpg 1260w,\n/static/42423f1ce6c0a3c6028a618434789650/eea4a/quickmaskmode.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>To do that, switch to Brush from the Tool panel or simply press B on your keyboard. To edit the mask, paint the areas that you want to select by using the colors Black or White.</p>\n<p>Note: the painted areas will then come out as Red and anything in this area will be hidden and will be part of the color change later. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b8750edab9980bbee37ff306066909a6/eea4a/standardmode.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 59.49367088607595%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"quick mask mode\"\n        title=\"quick mask mode\"\n        src=\"/static/b8750edab9980bbee37ff306066909a6/828fb/standardmode.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b8750edab9980bbee37ff306066909a6/ff44c/standardmode.jpg 158w,\n/static/b8750edab9980bbee37ff306066909a6/a6688/standardmode.jpg 315w,\n/static/b8750edab9980bbee37ff306066909a6/828fb/standardmode.jpg 630w,\n/static/b8750edab9980bbee37ff306066909a6/0ede0/standardmode.jpg 945w,\n/static/b8750edab9980bbee37ff306066909a6/3ac88/standardmode.jpg 1260w,\n/static/b8750edab9980bbee37ff306066909a6/eea4a/standardmode.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>when you follow 